  </item><item>
    <title>Kahn&#039;s Algorithm</title>
    <link>https://dxing.blog/Algorithms/Kahn's-Algorithm</link>
    <guid>https://dxing.blog/Algorithms/Kahn's-Algorithm</guid>
    <description><![CDATA[ Kahn’s Algorithm is an algorithm that finds a topological sort of a directed acyclic graph G=(V,E) in \mathcal{O}(|V|+|E|) time and \mathcal{O}(|V|) space. ]]></description>
    <pubDate>Sat, 27 Jun 2026 09:02:07 GMT</pubDate>
